been six devastations spaced

00:41:23.730 --> 00:41:27.530 align:middle line:84%
at intervals of about
300 million years--

00:41:27.530 --> 00:41:28.200 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:41:28.200 --> 00:41:32.700 align:middle line:84%
>>CREMO: --in the current
