>>CREMO: 300 million.

00:47:02.470 --> 00:47:03.095 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:47:03.095 --> 00:47:03.932 align:middle line:90%
>>CREMO: Oh, sure.

00:47:03.932 --> 00:47:05.890 align:middle line:84%
There's hundreds of
