00:55:11.331 --> 00:55:13.190 align:middle line:84%
some kind of link
between his consciousness

00:55:13.190 --> 00:55:16.910 align:middle line:84%
and the consciousness of
these departed personalities.

00:55:16.910 --> 00:55:17.417 align:middle line:90%
And then--

00:55:17.417 --> 00:55:18.250 align:middle line:90%
>>CREMO: Write out--

00:55:18.250 --> 00:55:18.720 align:middle line:90%
>>CREMO: --record--

00:55:18.720 --> 00:55:20.011 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: --what he was seeing.

00:55:20.011 --> 00:55:21.900 align:middle line:84%
>>CREMO: --write out
what they were seeing.

00:55:21.900 --> 00:55:28.030 align:middle line:84%
And it revealed the location
of an unknown chapel that

00:55:28.030 --> 00:55:32.710 align:middle line:84%
was part of that
cathedral complex.

00:55:32.710 --> 00:55:37.600 align:middle line:84%
And Frederick Bligh Bond
used this information

00:55:37.600 --> 00:55:39.250 align:middle line:90%
to guide his excavations.

00:55:39.250 --> 00:55:42.426 align:middle line:84%
And he confirmed
